reviewText: Ordered zone one USA and Canada, will not play in any brand player tried.

Just wanted to mention here as well that the region coding information on the listing is incorrect.  While this title is imported from the U.K., it is actually region free.  It is therefore playable in any U.S. player, plus you get it in a lovely steelbook!
This movie was real good. I enjoyed it very much. So did my child.
